# AI Task Execution Agent - Frontend

A modern React + Vite application for the AI Task Execution Agent.

## Setup

```bash
cd frontend
npm install
# or
pnpm install
```

## Development

```bash
npm run dev
```

Visit `http://localhost:5173`

## Backend

Make sure the backend is running on `http://localhost:5000` before starting the frontend.

The backend should have `OPENAI_API_KEY` set in `.env`.

## Features

- Create learning/productivity goals
- AI-powered structured task planning
- Daily task tracking with progress visualization
- Smart AI feedback and encouragement
- Personalized reminders
- Weekly performance reports
- JSON file-based progress tracking
